- In this thirdParty-directory get libarchive-library
(more information in: http://libarchive.orgi/)

git clone git://github.com/libarchive/libarchive

- step into libarchive directory
cd libarchive

- execute autogen.sh
build/autogen.sh

- type
pwd
- to get your path to this build folder

- then configure the installation prozess
./configure --prefix=<yourpathtothisthirdpartydirectory>/thirdParty/libarchive/build

- compile with
make 

- and install with
make install
